marketing: Made for the easy-riding highway lovers and the ramp-jumping adventure seekers, Pennzoil ® Motorcycle Premium Plus 10W-40 engine oil is full synthetic 4-stroke product formulated to protect and prolong engine life while reducing deposits caused by dirt particles. The high-quality synthetic Pennzoil® Motorcycle 10W-40 is made with natural gas base oil, combined with a motorcycle-specific additive pack with properties that helps to cleanse and keep the engine clean.
